      <sec>
        <title>Quantitative PCR Assays</title>
        <p>DNA protected from micrococcal nuclease digestion was quantified using an Applied Biosystems 7900HT realtime PCR machine. PCR conditions were 1Ã PCR buffer (Platinum Taq buffer, Invitrogen, CA), 3.5 mM MgCl<sub>2 </sub>0.2 mM dNTP mix, 0.4 <italic>Î¼</italic>M oligonucleotide primers, 1:20000 (v/v) SybrGreen, 0.025 U/<italic>Î¼</italic>l Platinum Taq. Nucleosome core samples were quantified against undigested genomic DNA standards.</p>
